snippet.title: TROLL AND I - FEATURES TRAILER
snippet.description: Discover the dynamic bond between Troll and Otto, two outcasts struggling to survive in the Nordic wilderness. Troll and I comes to PlayStation 4, Xbox One and PC on March 21, 2017. Learn more, including where to preorder, at www.trollandi.com.
